 {"id":"bd-1lg.12","title":"Unit tests: Animation physics engine","description":"Unit tests: Damped spring convergence to target (underdamped oscillates then settles, critically damped settles fastest, overdamped settles without oscillation). Animation completion detection. Time-step independence (same result regardless of dt granularity within tolerance). Zero-length animation handling. LOGGING SPEC: Assert animation.tick span. Property-based: all animations eventually complete (displacement and velocity below threshold).","status":"closed","priority":0,"issue_type":"task","assignee":"HazyCastle","created_at":"2026-02-13T18:01:13.139068252Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-02-25T02:12:35.101930536Z","closed_at":"2026-02-25T02:12:35.101912392Z","close_reason":"done","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"labels":["animation","ring3","test","unit"],"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"bd-1lg.12","depends_on_id":"bd-1lg","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-02-24T21:25:59Z","created_by":"import","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-1lg.12","depends_on_id":"bd-1lg.7","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-02-24T21:25:59Z","created_by":"import","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""}]}
 {"id":"bd-1lg.13","title":"E2E test: Full widget gallery rendering on 5 terminal emulators","description":"End-to-end test: Render every widget type (Table, List, Input, Tree, Tabs, Modal, CommandPalette, StatusBar, Progress, Sparkline, GalaxyBrain) on 5 terminal emulator configurations. Compare output against golden frames. p99 frame time < 8ms at 60fps for all scenarios. Test: (1) static rendering correctness, (2) interactive event handling, (3) resize behavior, (4) style/theme application. LOGGING SPEC: Full tracing subscriber. Assert complete span hierarchy per widget. Assert no ERROR/WARN logs during normal rendering. Assert frame_time_histogram p99 < 8ms.","status":"open","priority":0,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-02-13T18:01:13.248517081Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-02-13T18:10:29.042677644Z","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"labels":["e2e","gallery","ring3","test"],"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"bd-1lg.13","depends_on_id":"bd-1lg","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-02-24T21:25:59Z","created_by":"import","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-1lg.13","depends_on_id":"bd-1lg.1","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-02-24T21:25:59Z","created_by":"import","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-1lg.13","depends_on_id":"bd-1lg.17","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-02-24T21:25:59Z","created_by":"import","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-1lg.13","depends_on_id":"bd-1lg.19","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-02-24T21:25:59Z","created_by":"import","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-1lg.13","depends_on_id":"bd-1lg.2","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-02-24T21:25:59Z","created_by":"import","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-1lg.13","depends_on_id":"bd-1lg.20","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-02-24T21:25:59Z","created_by":"import","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-1lg.13","depends_on_id":"bd-1lg.21","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-02-24T21:25:59