 {"id":"bd-1lg.18","title":"Focus management system with tab order and trap","description":"Focus management: tab order (sequential, explicit order, skip), focus trap (modal dialogs trap focus), focus ring (wraps at boundaries), programmatic focus control, focus indicator styling. Focus state machine integrated with session types (section 5.2). TRACING: span 'focus.change' with fields: from_widget, to_widget, trigger. LOG: DEBUG for focus changes. METRICS: counter focus_changes_total.","status":"closed","priority":1,"issue_type":"feature","created_at":"2026-02-13T18:08:27.377301247Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-02-14T08:30:18.912896071Z","closed_at":"2026-02-14T08:30:18.912876354Z","close_reason":"Completed: Focus management system fully implemented with tab order, focus traps, focus ring wrapping, programmatic control, focus indicator styling (FocusIndicator with StyleOverlay/Underline/Border/None kinds), tracing instrumentation behind feature flag, and focus_change_count metric. All 2977 tests pass.","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"labels":["focus","management","ring3","widgets"],"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"bd-1lg.18","depends_on_id":"bd-1lg","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-02-24T21:25:59Z","created_by":"import","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-1lg.18","depends_on_id":"bd-1lg.1","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-02-24T21:25:59Z","created_by":"import","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""}]}
 {"id":"bd-1lg.19","title":"Tree widget with expand/collapse and lazy loading","description":"Tree widget: hierarchical node display, expand/collapse with keyboard (Enter/Space), lazy child loading for large trees, indent guides, icon support, search/filter within tree. Follows Elm Model/View/Update. TRACING: span 'tree.render' with fields: total_nodes, visible_nodes, expanded_count, render_duration_us. LOG: DEBUG for expand/collapse. METRICS: histogram tree_render_duration_us.","status":"closed","priority":1,"issue_type":"feature","assignee":"RainyWillow","created_at":"2026-02-13T18:09:11.997742038Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-02-18T20:51:09.418470816Z","closed_at":"2026-02-18T20:51:09.418452401Z","close_reason":"Completed tree widget feature implementation + regression fix + full validation","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"labels":["ring3","tree","widgets"],"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"bd-1lg.19","depends_on_id":"bd-1lg","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-02-24T21:25:59Z","created_by":"import","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-1lg.19","depends_on_id":"bd-1lg.1","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-02-24T21:25:59Z","created_by":"import","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""}],"comments":[{"id":166,"issue_id":"bd-1lg.19","author":"Dicklesworthstone","text":"Implemented tree widget feature set (keyboard Enter/Space toggle, mouse toggle/select, lazy child materialization, icon rendering, search query filter, tracing span+toggle logs+render metrics). Fresh-eyes audit fixed bug where search-filtered lazy descendants were dropped because filtered lazy nodes were not traversed; materialized filtered lazy matches into children and added regression test tree_search_query_includes_lazy_matching_descendants. Validation: cargo fmt --check, cargo test -p ftui-widgets --lib tree::tests:: -- --nocapture, cargo test -p ftui-widgets --all-targets -- --nocapture, cargo check --workspace --all-targets, cargo clippy --workspace --all-targets -- -D warnings.","created_at":"2026-02-18T20:51:06Z"}]}
 {"id":"bd-1lg.2","title":"Table widget with virtualized scrolling","description":"Table widget: column headers, sortable columns, row selection, keyboard navigation, virtualized row rendering (only render visible rows). Fenwick tree for O(log n) cumulative height lookup with variable row heights. Supports 100K+ rows without frame drops. TRACING: span 'table.render' with fields: total_rows, visible_rows, scroll_offset, sort_column, render_duration_us. LOG: DEBUG for scroll/sort events. METRICS: histogram table_visible_rows, gauge table_total_rows.","status":"closed","priority":0,"issue_type":"feature","created_at":"2026-02-13T18:01:11.711806001Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-02-14T04:25:48.164753798Z","closed_at":"2026-02-14T04:25:48.164734061Z","close_reason":"Already implemented: Table widget with Fenwick tree virtualization exists in ftui-widgets","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"labels":["ring3","table","virtualized","widgets"],"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"bd-1lg.2","depends_on_id":"bd-1lg","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-02-24T21:25:59Z","created_by":"import","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-1lg.2","depends_on_id":"bd-1lg.1","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-02-24T21:25:59Z","created_by":"import","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-1lg.2","depends_on_id":"bd-1q5.1","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-02-24T21:25:59Z","created_by":"import","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""}]}
 {"id":"bd-1lg.20","title":"List widget with selection and search filter","description":"List widget: single/multi select, keyboard navigation (j/k/arrows), search filter (incremental narrowing), scroll indicator, empty state display. Follows Elm Model/View/Update. TRACING: span 'list.render' with fields: total_items, visible_items, selected_count, filter_active, render_duration_us. LOG: DEBUG for selection changes.","status":"closed","priority":1,"issue_type":"feature","assignee":"RainyWillow","created_at":"2026-02-13T18:09:12.140271790Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-02-18T21:00:42.025156259Z","closed_at":"2026-02-18T21:00:42.025134889Z","close_reason":"Completed list widget selection/filter feature set with tracing and tests","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"labels":["list","ring3","widgets"],"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"bd-1lg.20","depends_on_id":"bd-1lg","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-02-24T21:25:59Z","created_by":"import","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-1lg.20","depends_on_id":"bd-1lg.1","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-02-24T21:25:59Z","created_by":"import","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""}],"comments":[{"id":167,"issue_id":"bd-1lg.20","author":"Dicklesworthstone","text":"Implemented list widget feature completion:
