 {"id":"bd-1lg.21","title":"Tabs widget with keyboard switching and overflow","description":"Tabs widget: horizontal tab bar, keyboard switching (left/right arrows, number keys), overflow scrolling for many tabs, closeable tabs, tab reordering. Follows Elm Model/View/Update. TRACING: span 'tabs.render' with fields: tab_count, active_tab, overflow, render_duration_us. LOG: DEBUG for tab switches.","status":"closed","priority":1,"issue_type":"feature","assignee":"RainyWillow","created_at":"2026-02-13T18:09:12.277192055Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-02-18T21:06:43.442501937Z","closed_at":"2026-02-18T21:06:43.442483302Z","close_reason":"Completed tabs widget implementation with keyboard/overflow/tracing/tests","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"labels":["ring3","tabs","widgets"],"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"bd-1lg.21","depends_on_id":"bd-1lg","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-02-24T21:25:59Z","created_by":"import","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-1lg.21","depends_on_id":"bd-1lg.1","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-02-24T21:25:59Z","created_by":"import","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""}],"comments":[{"id":169,"issue_id":"bd-1lg.21","author":"Dicklesworthstone","text":"Implemented a new tabs widget module and integrated it into ftui-widgets:
- added new file crates/ftui-widgets/src/tabs.rs and exports in crates/ftui-widgets/src/lib.rs
- horizontal tab bar rendering with active tab styling
- keyboard switching support: left/right arrows and number keys 1..9
- overflow handling with left/right markers and viewport offset tracking
- closeable tabs support (close_active)
- tab reordering helpers (move_active_left, move_active_right)
- mouse selection/activation support via hit regions
- tracing span tabs.render with tab_count, active_tab, overflow, render_duration_us
- debug log event for switching: message=tabs.switch
- comprehensive tests for rendering, keyboard switching, overflow, close/reorder, hit regions, and tracing

Validation:
- cargo fmt --check
