- cargo test -p ftui-widgets --lib --features tracing tabs::tests::tabs_tracing_span_and_switch_event_emitted -- --nocapture
- cargo test -p ftui-widgets --all-targets -- --nocapture
- cargo clippy -p ftui-widgets --all-targets -- -D warnings
- cargo check --workspace --all-targets
- cargo clippy --workspace --all-targets -- -D warnings","created_at":"2026-02-18T21:06:38Z"}]}
 {"id":"bd-1lg.22","title":"Modal dialog widget with focus trap and backdrop","description":"Modal widget: overlay dialog, focus trapping (Tab stays within modal), backdrop rendering, Escape to dismiss, configurable actions (OK/Cancel/Custom), z-order management. Follows Elm Model/View/Update. TRACING: span 'modal.render' with fields: modal_type, focus_trapped, backdrop_active, render_duration_us. LOG: DEBUG for modal open/close.","status":"closed","priority":1,"issue_type":"feature","assignee":"RainyWillow","created_at":"2026-02-13T18:09:12.417727080Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-02-18T19:53:26.725276148Z","closed_at":"2026-02-18T19:53:26.725258034Z","close_reason":"Completed modal tracing span + debug open/close logs; verified ftui-widgets gates","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"labels":["modal","ring3","widgets"],"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"bd-1lg.22","depends_on_id":"bd-1lg","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-02-24T21:25:59Z","created_by":"import","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-1lg.22","depends_on_id":"bd-1lg.1","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-02-24T21:25:59Z","created_by":"import","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-1lg.22","depends_on_id":"bd-1lg.18","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-02-24T21:25:59Z","created_by":"import","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""}],"comments":[{"id":170,"issue_id":"bd-1lg.22","author":"RainyWillow","text":"Implemented tracing/logging for modals (feature-gated behind ftui-widgets feature tracing).

- Added StackModal::modal_type() default label for spans/logs.
- ModalStack::render: span modal.render with fields modal_type, focus_trapped, backdrop_active, and recorded render_duration_us.
- ModalStack::push_with_focus/pop/pop_id/handle_event: DEBUG logs on open/close with modal_id, modal_type, depth, and (where applicable) result data.

Also updated widget tests impacted by Block::bordered() default padding and virtualized paging/partial-visibility semantics so ftui-widgets stays green.

